trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""></xref> element (compositor) from the XML Schema as specified by the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C).
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""> </xref> World Wide Web Consortium (W3C)에 지정 된 대로 XML 스키마에서 요소 (compositor).

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""></xref> allows only one of its children to appear in an instance.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""> </xref> 인스턴스에 표시 되도록 자식 중 하나에 허용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaChoice"></xref> class.

Gets the collection of the elements contained with the compositor (<xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""></xref>): <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaElement" name="XmlSchemaElement" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaGroupRef" name="XmlSchemaGroupRef" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaChoice" name="XmlSchemaChoice" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaSequence" name="XmlSchemaSequence" href=""></xref>, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaAny" name="XmlSchemaAny" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 작성자와 포함 된 요소의 컬렉션을 가져옵니다 (<xref uid="langword_csharp_choice" name="choice" href=""></xref>): <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaElement" name="XmlSchemaElement" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaGroupRef" name="XmlSchemaGroupRef" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaChoice" name="XmlSchemaChoice" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaSequence" name="XmlSchemaSequence" href=""> </xref>, 또는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaAny" name="XmlSchemaAny" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The collection of elements contained within <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaChoice" name="XmlSchemaChoice" href=""></xref>.
